729861f-a.title: Richmond: Victory Boulevard - Seneca Avenue
729861f-a.text:
Victory Boulevard, at the S.W. corner of Seneca
Avenue, showing James G. Carey's Sunnyside Garage. In the
background is the stack of the pumping station of the Depart-
ment of Water Supply.
June, 1927
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS
